Php to BTC, ETH, BCH and XRP.

BUYing crypto is so expensive that is added more amounts from the price level in world crypto market.

SELLing crypto is a little cheaper than the world price level.

Check this
WOLRD MARKET (sept 26, 2020)
ETH TO PHP (sell) 16,947 (as of 6:34pm mnl time)
PHP TO ETH (buy) 16,943 (same time)

COINS.PH: (same time and date)
ETH TO PHP (sell) 16,407.51
PHP TO ETH (buy) 17,113.99

Look at the difference!
They got 706.48 from your activity. (That is cheaper than the usual commissions they got, sometimes thousand.
